The **Employee Provident Fund (EPF)** is a mandatory retirement savings scheme for salaried employees in India, managed by EPFO. Employee contributes 12% of basic salary + DA, employer matches with 12% (3.67% to EPF, 8.33% to EPS). Current EPF interest rate is 8.25% p.a., making it one of the best risk-free returns available.
